edu.cpp.cs.cs141.prog_final

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cpp.cs.cs141.prog_final.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the player. The player has a certain amount of lives, defined by MAX_LIVES, an amount of turn they're invincible for, defined by INVINCIBLE_TURNS and a gun which has one bullet. The player can also die and respawn, reinitiallizing their attributes.
    Author:
    Corey Perez, Eduardo Saenz, Lance Dall, Grant Posner, Bumjoong Kim, Jacob Chong
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
